In the Matter of the Estate of Roberta W. Seaman, Deceased. Charlotte L. Gaynor, Appellant; William H. Baxter et al., Respondents.

Appeal unanimously dismissed without costs (see, Agee v Ajar, 154 AD2d 569). (Appeal from decree of Onondaga County Surrogate’s Court, Wells, S.—testamentary letters.) Present—Dillon, P. J., Doerr, Boomer, Lawton and Davis, JJ.
